1. Stojim u  *ugu* prostorije. (I'm standing in the *corner* of the room.)
2. *Uglovi* ovog pravougaonika su pravi. (The *angles* of this rectangle are right.)
3. Možemo li promeniti *ugao* kamere? (Can we change the *angle* of the camera?)
4. Neka ta stvar bude smeštena u donjem levom *uglu* ormara. (Let that thing be placed in the bottom left *corner* of the cabinet.)
5. *Ugaoni* kauč je veoma udoban. (The *corner* sofa is very comfortable.)
6. Ona je *ugao* u ovoj zgradi. (She is a *pillar* in this building.)
7. Slikao sam zalazak sunca iz različitih *uglova*. (I took a picture of the sunset from different *angles*.)
8. *Ugao* gledanja je veoma važan u fotografiji. (The *angle* of view is very important in photography.)
9. Pogledajte ovaj trougao. On ima tri *ugla*. (Look at this triangle. It has three *angles*.)
10. Potrebno je popraviti *uglom* sto u trpezariji. (The *corner* of the dining table needs to be fixed.)